      Chang Ho, in INEEL's Spot Light

     We are pleased to shine the spot light on Chang Oh and his long
     history of making significant, original contributions in the field of
     nuclear reactor safety. The American Society of Mechanical Engineers
     has named Chang a Fellow of the ASME in recognition of his
     contributions. more..

